      "span_text": "Borghesi et al.  reported that these same endothelial progenitor cells were in lower numbers in cord blood of preterm infants who subsequently developed BPD. These observations in infants at risk of BPD are starting points for recovery of stem cells from infants for growth in vitro for treatment with those cells or media from those cells."
